  "text": "We can model the above hider-seeker game as a multi-round zero-sum network interdiction game [CITATION_1] . For a given a road network G, the couriers seek to deliver goods on time whilst hiding from the attacker. The attacker on the other hand is an interdictor who aims to interdict (ambush) as many couriers as possible.",
